metadata.name: Freedom
metadata.description:
Laughter is an act of love, sometimes voluntary and other times spontaneous, like collage ;), Especially #collageminimal. To #CollageLovers and #ArtLovers.

Parallel lives that intersect in an image. ;) @2FotosCollage always combines two images or videos to create a new concept in a minimal collage possible.

We didn't always have the same #freedom to #wear more or less #fabric

Briefing: "CLOTH".

#2FotosCollage
